### ==========================================
### ASSIGNMENT API TESTS
### ==========================================

### Get All Assignments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments?page=0&size=100

###

### Create Assignment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "assetId": 1,
  "assignedDate": "2026-07-05",
  "expectedReturnDate": "2027-07-05",
  "notes": "Primary development laptop assignment."
}

###

### Create Second Assignment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 2,
  "assetId": 2,
  "assignedDate": "2026-07-05",
  "expectedReturnDate": "2026-12-31",
  "notes": "QA engineer workstation assignment."
}

###

### Return Asset
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments/1/return

###

### Try Assign Already Assigned Asset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 3,
  "assetId": 1,
  "assignedDate": "2026-07-05",
  "expectedReturnDate": "2026-10-01",
  "notes": "This request should fail because asset is already assigned."
}

###

### Get Assignments Again
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments?page=0&size=100